Feature: As a user I want to go to the Mattelsa page
  and add a product in the cart.

  Scenario Outline: As user I'm going to go to the Mattelsa page
    Given As a user I will enter one of the <categories> that appear on the page
    When  And I will select the cheapest clothes by selecting the <quantity> and <size>
    Then  Validate the total price of the product
    Examples:
      | categories | quantity | size |
      | Hombre     | 1        | 26   |
      | Mujer      | 1        | 24   |


